Description:
    Create files for adding a new screen to the application.

Example:
    rails generate screen FoodAssistance

    This will create:
        app/forms/food_assistance_form.rb
        app/controllers/food_assistance_controller.rb
        app/views/food_assistance/edit.html.erb
        spec/forms/food_assistance_form_spec.rb
        spec/controllers/food_assistance_controller_spec.rb

